Information
------------------------------

Deadly Instincts: Natural Born Killers
The law of the wild is kill or be killed - but how do different creatures execute this most grisly of tasks? From solo slayers like tigers - who rely on stealth, speed and strength - to team players like orcas - who use their intelligence to work together and kill against the odds - this is a new and unique exploration of how animals kill.
